headline: Apartments.com Releases Multifamily Rent Growth Report for September 2025
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., October 09, 2025--Today Apartments.com, an industry-leading online marketplace of CoStar Group (NASDAQ: CSGP), published its latest report on multifamily rent trends for September 2025.

headline: A pulse check on US hotel performance in a challenged economy
summary: At the 2025 Lodging Conference, executives and economists shared “a tale of two industries,” where economic turmoil affects different hotel consumer groups in starkly different ways.
